**/.pytest_cache
**/.coverage
**/htmlcov
**/.tox

# IDEs
**/.vscode
**/.idea
**/*.swp
**/*.swo

# Environment & secrets
**/.env
**/.env.local
**/.env.*.local

# Build artefacts
**/dist
**/build
**/*.egg-info
**/*.egg
**/MANIFEST

# Type checkers & linters
**/.mypy_cache
**/.ruff_cache

# OS
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db

